  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Level 2</strong> Transmutation</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> undefined touch</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (a drop of bitumen and a spider)</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> Concentration, up to 1 hour</p>\n\nUntil the spell ends, one willing creature you touch gains the ability to move up, down, and across vertical surfaces and along ceilings, while leaving its hands free. The target also gains a Climb Speed|XPHB equal to its Speed|XPHB.\n\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> You can target one additional creature for each spell slot level above 2.</p>",
